creator: ZippyYum
descriptionHtml:
SubOps is a tablet-based app built to optimize your restaurant's operations. The app features our ultra-smart prepping scheduler to help you determine when and how much to prep each day! The app also pairs with ZippyYum's wireless GoLabel printer for effortless food prepping labels.

• Smart algorithms suggest how much to prep
• Uses sales and inventory metrics for calculations
• Determines how much and when to prep during the day
• Built-in training materials for food prepping
• Training videos and instructions built for your restaurant
• Pairs wirelessly with the GoLabel printer
• Print easy-to-read and scannable food prep labels
• Knows what food items you prep
descriptionShort: SubOps takes the guesswork out of prep work and optimizes your store operations!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Release notes:

Ability to assign tasks to users on a daily basis in the Checklist module
Ability to configure Bottles/Containers in the prepping module
Several bugs and enhancements


For any questions, comments and suggestions, please reach out to support.
